.TH smi-nics-location "1" "October 2025" "SMI Toolset 0.100.0" "SMI Base Command"
.SH NAME
smi-nics-location \- Print the SMI network interfaces configuration path (Deprecated)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B smi-nics-location
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
.B smi-nics-location
is a deprecated command that prints the path to the network interfaces (nics) configuration directory within the SMI localhost location.
